Package: caugi
Title: Causal Graph Interface
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Frederik", "Fabricius-Bjerre", , "frederik@fabriciusbjerre.dk", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create, query, and modify causal graphs. 'caugi' (Causal Graph
Interface) is a causality-first, high performance graph package that provides a 
simple interface to build, structure, and examine causal relationships in R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://frederikfabriciusbjerre.github.io/caugi/
